channel.title: *~Pancakes Pk Dev Team~*
channel.description:
Pancakes Pk Returns With New Twists And Turns... can you handle it?
Pancakes Pk V.3
Im not sure if you renember pancakes pk or not, but it was fun. with the arise of the new silab client i decieded to bring back pancakes pk to pleasure the players of Silabsoft.
I have a clean base for a new server. its Pimpscape Non-pk. it has many stats, and many cool features. its also very flexible. I need a design team to help me out and build this server with me. i can handle building a server, ive proven it before, but my problem is i dont have many ideas, and i cant stay motivated for long. if you would like to help me bring back this fun server, please register to my forums at: (in Sig)
also reply to this post with the following information:
[code]email address: runescape lvl: can you code?: are you good at designing servers?: do you have time on your hands?: what time zone do you live in?: what country do you live in?: can anyone refer you as a good developer?: anything else you would like to say?:[/code]
